{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had-- they had gold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they-- they knew what they are doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the beating-- well, we were working around there, in that factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were only 20 meters away from where the beatings took place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put on records all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They played country music and jazz music to try to block out the horrible cries.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was terribly painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- they were putting nails into their-- I mean, into their fingers, and I know the man got beaten in their-- the testicles got beaten with rubber truncheons and the fact is that when we went back from work in the evening-- well, we didn't-- we didn't have to tell these stories.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because all the people-- the man-- the people who were beaten all day-- they were delivered on stretcher at nighttime.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And most of them died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when this-- I know-- I remember this, when-- when all these dying, and dying or dead people, were delivered back to their families, to their wives and children, and all the others stood around them, and a lot of them went home and took poison right away.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they killed themselves, because they knew it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you see a solicitor coming back, beaten to pulp, the other one knows that tomorrow it will be my turn, so they quickly killed themselves-- killed the wife and then they took it together, husband and wife.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, there were lots and lots of suicides, dead bodies where I was staying, in that sector.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- I mean, the Hungarian gendarmes were desperate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because they knew it, that the Germans will start the next transport in two days, and the other one in three days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they only had three, four days to make their money.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
